  <brief_title>The Effect of Doxycycline on Matrix Metalloproteinase Expression and Activity in the Abdominal Aneurysm</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Doxycycline on Matrix Metalloproteinase Expression and Activity in the Abdominal Aneurysm</official_title>
